HEADWORD: Budlet
<hw>Bud"let</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Bud</ets> +
<ets>-let</ets>.]</ety> <def>A little bud springing from a parent
bud.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We have a criterion to distinguish one bud from another, or the
parent bud from the numerous <qex>budlets</qex> which are its
offspring.</q> <rj><qau>E. Darwin.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Budorcas</ent>⟦br⟧
